From f0dc53a7b77f900aa3d13309f84912b324ccca35 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ping-Ke Shih <pkshih@realtek.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Jan 2025 15:28:21 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: rtw89: phy: rename to RTW89_PHY_NUM as proper naming
Git-commit: f0dc53a7b77f900aa3d13309f84912b324ccca35
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

The meaning is number of PHY, not maximum ID of PHY. Change to proper
naming.

No change logic at all.

Signed-off-by: Ping-Ke Shih <pkshih@realtek.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250117072828.16728-2-pkshih@realtek.com
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

